column2: SELECT TOP # s.SpecObjID, s.z,   L1.ew, L1.ewErr, L1.continuum,   L2.ew, L2.ewErr, L2.continuum,   S.petroMag_r INTO mydb.Try1  FROM SpecObj as S,   SpecLine as L1,   SpecLine as L2 WHERE S.specClass = #   AND S.SpecObjID = L1.SpecObjID   AND S.SpecObjID = L2.SpecObjID   AND L1.LineId = #   AND L2.LineId = #   AND L1.ew/nullif(L1.ewErr,#)>#   AND L2.ew/nullif(L2.ewErr,#)>#
